# 9. Functional Requirements

## Lead Capture

### BR-01

The system shall capture leads from website forms, social media campaigns, phone inquiries, and showroom visits.

### BR-02

The system shall automatically create a lead record upon receipt of customer information.

### BR-03

The system shall validate mandatory customer fields before lead creation.

---

## Lead Assignment

### BR-04

The system shall automatically assign leads based on dealership location.

### BR-05

The system shall notify assigned sales representatives immediately after lead assignment.

### BR-06

The system shall allow sales managers to manually reassign leads when required.

---

## Lead Qualification

### BR-07

The system shall support lead qualification based on predefined criteria.

### BR-08

The system shall capture customer vehicle preferences and purchase intent.

### BR-09

The system shall allow sales representatives to update lead status.

---

## Follow-Up Management

### BR-10

The system shall automatically create follow-up tasks.

### BR-11

The system shall generate reminders for overdue follow-ups.

### BR-12

The system shall maintain communication history for each lead.

---

## Test Drive Scheduling

### BR-13

The system shall allow scheduling of vehicle test drives.

### BR-14

The system shall send confirmation notifications to customers.

### BR-15

The system shall track test drive completion status.

---

## Reporting & Analytics

### BR-16

The system shall provide lead conversion reports.

### BR-17

The system shall provide sales performance dashboards.

### BR-18

The system shall provide lead source effectiveness reports.

### BR-19

The system shall provide branch-level performance reports.

